          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1661865957264-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash the <strong>gem lettuces</strong>,<strong> </strong>then remove the <strong>outer leaves</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Shred the<strong> inner core</strong></p><p>Peel and grate (don't chop!) the<strong> garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1661866004262-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1661866004262-x400.jpg",
