            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>grated garlic </strong>and most of the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> to the bowl with the <strong>remaining butter curry paste</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> white wine vinegar</strong>,<strong> </strong>1 tbsp<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </strong>[2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tbsp<strong> </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spiced Caesar dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
